description: A dashboard for visualizing results from the k6.io load testing tool by groups, using the InfluxDB exporter.Based on https://grafana.com/dashboards/10660

targets.query: SELECT mean("value") FROM "errors" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

panels.description: Grouped by 1 sec intervals and group name
panels.title: $Measurement (over time per group)

panels.description: Grouped by 1 sec intervals and group name
panels.title: $Measurement (over time per tag)

targets.query: SELECT count("value"), min("value"), median("value"), max("value"), mean("value"), percentile("value", 50) AS "P50" , percentile("value", 90) AS "P90", percentile("value", 95) AS "P95", percentile("value", 99) AS "P99", percentile("value", 99.9) AS "P99.9" FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE ("group" =~ /^$Group$/ AND "name" =~ /^$Tag$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "group"

SELECT count("value"), min("value"), median("value"), max("value"), mean("value"), percentile("value", 50) AS "P50" , percentile("value", 90) AS "P90", percentile("value", 95) AS "P95", percentile("value", 99) AS "P99", percentile("value", 99.9) AS "P99.9"FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE ("group" =~ /^$Group$/ AND "name" =~ /^$Tag$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"

list.label: Group
list.name: Group
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES WITH KEY = "group" WHERE $timeFilter

list.label: Tag
list.name: Tag
list.query: SHOW TAG VALUES WITH KEY = "name" WHERE $timeFilter
